Grimlock stomped towards Branded, and snarled, and inhuman noise. "You
think that stop me Grimlock. ME TEAR OUT YOUR SPARK, AND EAT IT RAW" he
growled, opening his mouth, and emmiting a large beam of his laser
breath, at the arm holding the weapon.
